# NOTE: frontend/dist/ is intentionally NOT git-ignored. databricks sync uses
# .gitignore to decide what to upload, and the built SPA must reach the
# workspace for Databricks Apps to serve it. If you don't want to commit
# build output, add it to .git/info/exclude (per-clone, not shared).